{"tha-ap399:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap399:0.2":"Pilindavacchavagga ","tha-ap399:0.3":"Girimanandattheraapadana ","tha-ap399:1.1":"“Bhariya me kalankata, ","tha-ap399:1.2":"putto sivathikam gato; ","tha-ap399:1.3":"Mata pita mata bhata, ","tha-ap399:1.4":"ekacitamhi dayhare. ","tha-ap399:2.1":"Tena sokena santatto, ","tha-ap399:2.2":"kiso pandu ahosaham; ","tha-ap399:2.3":"Cittakkhepo ca me asi, ","tha-ap399:2.4":"tena sokena attito. ","tha-ap399:3.1":"Sokasallaparetoham, ","tha-ap399:3.2":"vanantamupasankamim; ","tha-ap399:3.3":"Pavattaphalam bhunjitva, ","tha-ap399:3.4":"rukkhamule vasamaham. ","tha-ap399:4.1":"Sumedho nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap399:4.2":"dukkhassantakaro jino; ","tha-ap399:4.3":"Mamuddharitukamo so, ","tha-ap399:4.4":"aganchi mama santikam. ","tha-ap399:5.1":"Padasaddam sunitvana, ","tha-ap399:5.2":"sumedhassa mahesino; ","tha-ap399:5.3":"Paggahetvanaham sisam, ","tha-ap399:5.4":"ullokesim mahamunim. ","tha-ap399:6.1":"Upagate mahavire, ","tha-ap399:6.2":"piti me udapajjatha; ","tha-ap399:6.3":"Tadasimekaggamano, ","tha-ap399:6.4":"disva tam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap399:7.1":"Satim patilabhitvana, ","tha-ap399:7.2":"pannamutthimadasaham; ","tha-ap399:7.3":"Nisidi bhagava tattha, ","tha-ap399:7.4":"anukampaya cakkhuma. ","tha-ap399:8.1":"Nisajja tattha bhagava, ","tha-ap399:8.2":"sumedho lokanayako; ","tha-ap399:8.3":"Dhammam me kathayi buddho, ","tha-ap399:8.4":"sokasallavinodanam. ","tha-ap399:9.1":"‘Anavhita tato agum, ","tha-ap399:9.2":"ananunnata ito gata; ","tha-ap399:9.3":"Yathagata tatha gata, ","tha-ap399:9.4":"tattha ka paridevana. ","tha-ap399:10.1":"Yathapi pathika satta, ","tha-ap399:10.2":"vassamanaya vutthiya; ","tha-ap399:10.3":"Sabhanda upagacchanti, ","tha-ap399:10.4":"vassassapatanaya te. ","tha-ap399:11.1":"Vasse ca te oramite, ","tha-ap399:11.2":"sampayanti yadicchakam; ","tha-ap399:11.3":"Evam mata pita tuyham, ","tha-ap399:11.4":"tattha ka paridevana. ","tha-ap399:12.1":"Agantuka pahunaka, ","tha-ap399:12.2":"caliteritakampita; ","tha-ap399:12.3":"Evam mata pita tuyham, ","tha-ap399:12.4":"tattha ka paridevana. ","tha-ap399:13.1":"Yathapi urago jinnam, ","tha-ap399:13.2":"hitva gacchati sam tacam; ","tha-ap399:13.3":"Evam mata pita tuyham, ","tha-ap399:13.4":"sam tanum idha hiyare’. ","tha-ap399:14.1":"Buddhassa giramannaya, ","tha-ap399:14.2":"sokasallam vivajjayim; ","tha-ap399:14.3":"Pamojjam janayitvana, ","tha-ap399:14.4":"buddhasettham avandaham. ","tha-ap399:15.1":"Vanditvana mahanagam, ","tha-ap399:15.2":"Pujayim girimanjarim; ","tha-ap399:15.3":"Dibbagandham sampavantam, ","tha-ap399:15.4":"Sumedham lokanayakam. ","tha-ap399:16.1":"Pujayitvana sambuddham, ","tha-ap399:16.2":"sire katvana anjalim; ","tha-ap399:16.3":"Anussaram gunaggani, ","tha-ap399:16.4":"santhavim lokanayakam. ","tha-ap399:17.1":"‘Nittinnosi mahavira, ","tha-ap399:17.2":"sabbannu lokanayaka; ","tha-ap399:17.3":"Sabbe satte uddharasi, ","tha-ap399:17.4":"nanena tvam mahamune. ","tha-ap399:18.1":"Vimatim dvelhakam vapi, ","tha-ap399:18.2":"sanchindasi mahamune; ","tha-ap399:18.3":"Patipadesi me maggam, ","tha-ap399:18.4":"tava nanena cakkhuma. ","tha-ap399:19.1":"Araha vasipatta ca, ","tha-ap399:19.2":"chalabhinna mahiddhika; ","tha-ap399:19.3":"Antalikkhacara dhira, ","tha-ap399:19.4":"parivarenti tavade. ","tha-ap399:20.1":"Patipanna ca sekha ca, ","tha-ap399:20.2":"phalattha santi savaka; ","tha-ap399:20.3":"Surodayeva paduma, ","tha-ap399:20.4":"pupphanti tava savaka. ","tha-ap399:21.1":"Mahasamuddovakkhobho, ","tha-ap399:21.2":"atulopi duruttaro; ","tha-ap399:21.3":"Evam nanena sampanno, ","tha-ap399:21.4":"appameyyosi cakkhuma’. ","tha-ap399:22.1":"Vanditvaham lokajinam, ","tha-ap399:22.2":"cakkhumantam mahayasam; ","tha-ap399:22.3":"Puthu disa namassanto, ","tha-ap399:22.4":"patikutiko aganchaham. ","tha-ap399:23.1":"Devaloka cavitvana, ","tha-ap399:23.2":"sampajano patissato; ","tha-ap399:23.3":"Okkamim matuya kucchim, ","tha-ap399:23.4":"sandhavanto bhavabhave. ","tha-ap399:24.1":"Agara abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap399:24.2":"pabbajim anagariyam; ","tha-ap399:24.3":"Atapi nipako jhayi, ","tha-ap399:24.4":"patisallanagocaro. ","tha-ap399:25.1":"Padhanam padahitvana, ","tha-ap399:25.2":"tosayitva mahamunim; ","tha-ap399:25.3":"Candovabbhaghana mutto, ","tha-ap399:25.4":"vicarami aham sada. ","tha-ap399:26.1":"Vivekamanuyuttomhi, ","tha-ap399:26.2":"upasanto nirupadhi; ","tha-ap399:26.3":"Sabbasave parinnaya, ","tha-ap399:26.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap399:27.1":"Timsakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap399:27.2":"yam buddhamabhipujayim; ","tha-ap399:27.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap399:27.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap399:28.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap399:28.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap399:28.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap399:28.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap399:29.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap399:29.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap399:29.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap399:30.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap399:30.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap399:30.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap399:31.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma girimanando thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap399:32.1":"Girimanandattherassapadanam sattamam. "}